 method for recovering spontaneous emission.
 We formulate the method in terms of a two-level system in a 1D and 3D space.
 Our results suggest that this new approach can indeed recover the correct
 spontaneous emission rate, as well as accurately capture both intensity
 and coherent emission using an ensemble of classical trajectories that
 simulate the statistical variations of a quantum electrodynamics field.
 
